social_posts.post_text: ✨Merry Christmas!! ✨ Happy holidays, everyone! I’m about ready to bark loudly for all to hear 🤗
Rainy days are for coffee shops on coffee shops! ☔️☕️ @overcastcoffeecompany
Found me a raincoat that doubles as a superhero cape 💁‍♂️🦄☔️
Thank you to @moira.moyed and her humans for taking such good care of me!! 🌯💕 I’m still a little mad at my humans for leaving but someday I’ll forgive them. 🤨
Happy birthday, @moira.moyed!! 🥰 🍩 thanks for being the best bestie a bear could ask for!
Beach bears! 😎☀️✨ @moira.moyed got lots of pets, I borked in lots of faces… it was a great day!
Getting noms at our new favorite, @sunnyupseattle! 🍳🥓😋 #baconbaconbacon We saw it was @worfy_floofy approved!
Today’s lunch break walkies: 5/5 for sniff options. 🌼🥲
Living my best life at @westseattlenursery today! 🥰 🌱 ☕️ #pupcup #westseattle
Pumpkin 🎃✨ patchin’ with @moira.moyed and her humans! #fall #autumnvibes
🪩✨ Happy New Year!! ✨🪩 Thank you @saywoofstudios for the fab new photos and snacks.

Big @seattlekraken fan energy! ✨🏒🥅 

Photo by the amazing @saywoofstudios
Will wait in the snow flurries for @xoxomotopizza any day!! ❄️🍕🤗 #pupperonie
